flowchart TD
    A[POST /dashboard/chat/\nwith message and session_id] --> B{Active McpSession\nexists for user}

    B -->|No| C[Create McpSession\ntokens_used = 0\ntokens_budget = UserProfile.mcp_token_budget\nor MCP_SESSION_TOKEN_BUDGET setting]
    B -->|Yes| D[Load McpSession\ntokens_used, tokens_budget]
    C --> D

    D --> E{tokens_used\n>= tokens_budget}

    E -->|Yes, exhausted| F[Return structured error response\nerror budget_exhausted, used N, budget M]
    F --> G[SSE budget_exhausted event to browser]
    G --> H[Chat panel shows exhaustion message\nwith Reset session link]

    E -->|No, budget available| I[Forward message to MCP Server\nvia Docker internal network\nwith shared-secret header]

    I --> J[MCP Server calls Claude API\nwith prefab tool definitions]

    J --> K{Claude API\nstop_reason}

    K -->|tool_use| L[Extract tool_name + tool_input]
    L --> M{widget_type in\nTextChoices enum\nConfig keys in\nallowed set}

    M -->|No, injection attempt| N[Return tool_result with is_error=true\nNo DB write occurs]
    N --> K

    M -->|Yes, valid call| O{Mutating tool\nadd / update / remove}

    O -->|Yes| P[POST /internal/dashboard/widgets/\nDashboard DB write via Django]
    O -->|No, read-only| Q[GET /internal/dashboard/widgets/\nRead-only DB query via Django]
    P --> R[Tool result returned to Claude]
    Q --> R
    R --> K

    K -->|end_turn| S[Receive final text response\nand token usage input_tokens + output_tokens]

    S --> T[token_delta = input_tokens + output_tokens]
    T --> U[DB McpSession.tokens_used += token_delta]

    U --> V{New tokens_used\n>= tokens_budget}

    V -->|Yes, now exhausted| W[Append budget warning to SSE stream\nToken indicator turns red in UI]
    V -->|No, still within budget| X[SSE text chunks\nwith tokens_used and tokens_budget]
    W --> X

    X --> Y[Browser update chat history\nand token indicator]
    Y --> Z{Dashboard\nmutated}

    Z -->|Yes| AA[Reload iframe\nGET /dashboard/render/id]
    Z -->|No| AB[Chat panel update only]
    AA --> END([End])
    AB --> END

    H --> END
